---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - MTL Partners LLC">
  <Navbar currentPage="/about" />
  <main class="pt-24">
    <section class="py-16 bg-charcoal-800">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-white">
          About MTL Partners
        </h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-charcoal-900">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">Company Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
          MTL Partners LLC is a UAE-based company registered in the Sharjah Free Zone.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          MTL Partners supports technical operations, system integration, and ongoing workflow management for partner organizations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-charcoal-800">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">Areas of support</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
          MTL Partners supports a range of technical and operational functions depending on the needs of each organization.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">This may include:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>System and tool integration</li>
          <li>Workflow organization and structure</li>
          <li>Technical operations support</li>
          <li>Ongoing system maintenance</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Support is provided on an ongoing basis and adapted to the specific environment and processes already in place.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-charcoal-900">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">Operating Model</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
          MTL Partners works directly with a small number of organizations on an ongoing basis.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          The company operates remotely and supports partners across different regions as needed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-charcoal-800">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">Company information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
          MTL Partners LLC is registered in the Sharjah Free Zone, United Arab Emirates.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <li>Established: 2025</li>
          <li>Operating model: Remote / international</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
